&lt;p&gt;This is a &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;full-time position&lt;/span&gt;, eligible for full benefits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your responsibilities:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ignore-global-css&quot;&gt;
