&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspire and motivate clients to reach their goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Model appropriate personal interaction and life skills at all times.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee and maintain joy and safety in community spaces.&lt;/li&gt;
