&lt;li&gt;Respond to emergencies appropriately, including contacting appropriate staff, and interacting and cooperating with police, fire, and medical personnel as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with other staff members to ensure the continuum of services for the clients.&lt;/li&gt;
