&lt;p&gt;Under the direction and guidance of the Program Manager, you will be responsible for guiding and counseling clients in our housing programs to ensure that they are on track to meet their goals. You may provide guidance to clients one-on-one or in groups.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;full-time position&lt;/span&gt;, eligible for full benefits.&lt;/p&gt;
