&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Any of our housing programs located throughout San Francisco.&amp;nbsp;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This may include sites in the Tenderloin neighborhood.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We have one housing site in the East Bay (Berkeley).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We have one licensed facility that serves clients under the age of 18. Otherwise, all of our programs serve Transitional Aged Youth (TAY), age 18-24.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
